Usage: writeTimingCon [-help] [<filename>] [-clocks <string>]
                      [-commands <string>]
                      [-exclude_annotated {delays checks transitions}]
                      [-pins <string>] [-view <viewName>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
<filename>                           # Specifes the name of the constraints
                                     # file (string, optional)
-clocks <string>                     # filter clocks (string, optional)
-commands <string>                   # filter commands (string, optional)
-exclude_annotated {delays checks transitions}
                                     # Disables listing of annotated
                                     # constraints (enum, optional)
-pins <string>                       # filter pins (string, optional)
-view <viewName>                     # Specifies a view name to obtain the
                                     # desired SDC (string, optional)